# Note: HSTS is authoritatively set at the Cloudflare edge (SSL/TLS → Edge
# Certificates → HSTS), which also covers the apex redirect. This line is a
# backup for www asset responses; keep the two max-age values roughly in sync.
/*
  Strict-Transport-Security: max-age=31536000; includeSubDomains
  X-Content-Type-Options: nosniff
  Referrer-Policy: strict-origin-when-cross-origin
